@startuml
!theme plain
title SD-03: 입질 및 물고기 낚기

actor Player
participant "FishSpawner\n<<IFishSpawner>>" as FS
participant "FishController\n<<IFish>>" as FC
participant "FloatController\n<<IFishingFloat>>" as FLC
participant "FishingRodController\n<<IFishingRod>>" as FRC
participant "TensionDataSO" as TD
participant "FeedbackManager\n<<IFeedbackService>>" as FM
participant "GameFlowManager\n<<IGameFlowManager>>" as GFM

== 입질 대기 ==
FS -> FS : StartBiteTimer()
FS -> FS : SelectFishByProbability()
note right: 어종별 확률 + 대기 시간 계산

...대기 시간 경과...

== 입질 발생 ==
FS -> FC : Initialize(speciesData)
activate FC
FC -> FC : weight, resistance 설정
FS --> FM : 예고 입질 이벤트
FM -> FM : ShowVisualEffect("Ripple", floatPos)
FM -> FM : PlayHaptic(LightPulse, Main)

...잠시 후 본 입질...

FS --> FRC : <<VoidEventSO>> BiteOccurred
FLC -> FLC : SinkingDepth 급격히 증가
FM -> FM : PlaySound("FloatSink")
FM -> FM : PlayHaptic(StrongPulse, Main)
TD -> TD : 장력 추적 활성화

== 챔질 판정 (Hooking Zone + 가속도 이중 조건) ==
FM -> FM : ShowVisualEffect("HookingZoneGuide")
note right: 입질 발생 시 챔질 존 가이드 표시\n(위로 올리라는 화살표 등)

alt 성공: hookTimingWindow 내 챔질
  Player -> FRC : LiftRod() [위로 드는 동작]
  FRC -> FRC : CheckHookingZone(controllerPos)
  note right: 조건 1: IsInHookingZone == true\n조건 2: Acceleration >= hookingMinAcceleration\n두 조건 동시 충족 시 성공

  alt 존 진입 (가속도 판정 전)
    FM -> FM : PlayHaptic(LightPulse, Main)
  end

  FRC -> FRC : JudgeHookSuccess()
  FRC -> FRC : state = Hit
  FM -> FM : PlayHaptic(StrongPulse, Main)
  FM -> FM : ShowVisualEffect("HookSuccess")
  FM -> FM : PlaySound("HookSuccess")

  FRC -> FRC : state = MiniGame
  FRC --> GFM : <<VoidEventSO>> RodStateChanged
  GFM -> GFM : TransitionTo(MiniGame)

else 실패: 타이밍 초과
  FC -> FC : 물고기 도망
  deactivate FC
  FM -> FM : PlayTTS("아쉽습니다. 다시 도전해보세요")
  FM -> FM : ShowVisualEffect("FishEscape")
  FRC -> FRC : state = Idle (롤백)
  FLC -> FLC : RetractLine()
  GFM -> GFM : TransitionTo(FishingReady)
end

@enduml